div.div:
An unknown voice disturbed me while I was levitating during my cultivation to reach the transcendent demonic state.
My concentration had been broken, and I fell into an unconscious, overloaded state. When I awoke a month later, the Lich King had already taken control of the Murim.
After the battle that ended with the destruction of the Heavenly Demon Cult, I awoke a hundred and forty years later in a Murim where magic and martial arts coexisted.

My name is Yu Il-Sin, a third-rate web novel author.
I discovered a strange gaming app and was judged to be a G-rank hunter. You save the world in the game and gain divine powers you can use in real life. It's a little bit strange, somehow?
My follower count and the number of quests keep increasing. In the midst of this, when should I write my web novel? It's suspended for personal reasons... No, I'm starting the serialization.
(Source: Naver, translated)
